        <headline>Heat Advisory issued August 8 at 9:51PM MDT until August 9 at 9:00PM MDT by NWS El Paso Tx/Santa Teresa NM</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Temperatures up to 105.

* WHERE...Southwest Desert/Mimbres Basin.

* WHEN...Until 9 PM MDT Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
